HEADWORD: Enopla
<hw>En"o*pla</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<?/ armed; <?/ in + <?/, pl., armor.]</ety> <fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld>
